c: 5
v: 4
t: "Bakubuuza ggwe (Nabbi Muhammad) ebibakkirizibwa (okulya), gamba nti mukkirizibwa okulya ebirungi, era (mukkirizibwa okulya) n’okulya ebyo ebikwatiddwa ebiyigga byemutendese nemuyigiriza ddala okusinziira nga Katonda bweyabayigiriza, bweguba gutyo mulye ebyo bye bibakwatira, era mubyogerereko erinnya lya Katonda (nga mubisindika okugenda okukwata ensolo) era mutye Katonda, anti mazima Katonda mwangu wa kubala"